@startuml SD_03_GoogleOAuth
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Đăng nhập Google OAuth 2.0
' FR-03: Đăng nhập/Đăng ký 1-click via Google
' ============================================================

title **SD-03: Đăng nhập Google OAuth 2.0\n(Social Login Flow)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    ParticipantBorderColor #1565C0
    ArrowColor #1565C0
}

actor "Guest" as User #LightGreen
participant "Browser" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "GoogleLoginServlet\n(Controller)" as LoginCtrl #E3F2FD
participant "GoogleCallbackServlet\n(Controller)" as CallbackCtrl #E3F2FD
participant "GoogleOAuthService" as OAuthSvc #E8F5E9
participant "UserService" as UserSvc #E8F5E9
participant "UserDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
box "External Services" #F5F5F5
    participant "Google\nOAuth 2.0" as Google #FFCDD2
end box
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Bước 1: Initiate OAuth Flow ==

User -> Browser: Click "Đăng nhập bằng Google"
Browser -> LoginCtrl: GET /auth/google/login
activate LoginCtrl

LoginCtrl -> OAuthSvc: getAuthorizationUrl()
activate OAuthSvc
OAuthSvc -> OAuthSvc: Build URL:\nhttps://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth\n?client_id={CLIENT_ID}\n&redirect_uri={CALLBACK_URL}\n&response_type=code\n&scope=openid email profile\n&state={CSRF_STATE}\n&access_type=offline
OAuthSvc --> LoginCtrl: authorizationUrl
deactivate OAuthSvc

LoginCtrl -> LoginCtrl: session.setAttribute(\n"oauth_state", state)
LoginCtrl --> Browser: HTTP 302 Redirect\n→ Google Authorization URL
deactivate LoginCtrl

Browser -> Google: Redirect to Google Login Page
activate Google
Google --> Browser: Google Consent Screen\n(Choose Account + Permissions)
Browser --> User: Chọn tài khoản Google

== Bước 2: User Authorizes ==

User -> Browser: Chọn tài khoản + Allow
Browser -> Google: Submit authorization
Google --> Browser: HTTP 302 Redirect\n→ /auth/google/callback\n?code={AUTH_CODE}&state={STATE}
deactivate Google

== Bước 3: Exchange Code for Tokens ==

Browser -> CallbackCtrl: GET /auth/google/callback\n?code={AUTH_CODE}&state={STATE}
activate CallbackCtrl

' --- Validate State (CSRF protection) ---
CallbackCtrl -> CallbackCtrl: Validate state parameter\nvs session oauth_state

alt #FFE0E0 State Mismatch (CSRF attack)
    CallbackCtrl --> Browser: Redirect → /login\n+ "Phiên đăng nhập không hợp lệ"
    Browser --> User: ⛔ Error page
else #E8F5E9 State Valid

    CallbackCtrl -> OAuthSvc: exchangeCodeForTokens(authCode)
    activate OAuthSvc

    OAuthSvc -> Google: POST https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token\n{code, client_id, client_secret,\nredirect_uri, grant_type=authorization_code}
    activate Google
    Google --> OAuthSvc: {\n  access_token: "ya29...",\n  id_token: "eyJ...",\n  refresh_token: "1//...",\n  expires_in: 3600\n}
    deactivate Google

    ' --- Get User Info ---
    OAuthSvc -> Google: GET https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v3/userinfo\nAuthorization: Bearer {access_token}
    activate Google
    Google --> OAuthSvc: {\n  sub: "1234567890",\n  email: "user@gmail.com",\n  name: "Nguyễn Văn A",\n  picture: "https://lh3...",\n  email_verified: true\n}
    deactivate Google

    OAuthSvc --> CallbackCtrl: GoogleUserInfo\n{email, name, picture, googleId}
    deactivate OAuthSvc

    == Bước 4: Find or Create User ==

    CallbackCtrl -> UserSvc: findOrCreateGoogleUser(\ngoogleUserInfo)
    activate UserSvc

    UserSvc -> DAO: findByEmail(email)
    activate DAO
    DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Users\nWHERE email = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> DAO: User or null
    deactivate DB
    DAO --> UserSvc: result
    deactivate DAO

    alt User NOT exists
        UserSvc -> UserSvc: Create new User:\nfullName = googleName\nemail = googleEmail\navatar = googlePicture\nrole = "customer"\noauthProvider = "google"\noauthId = googleSub\nisActive = true\npassword = null (OAuth user)

        UserSvc -> DAO: create(newUser)
        activate DAO
        DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO Users\n(userId, fullName, email, avatar,\nrole, oauthProvider, oauthId,\nisActive, createdAt)
        activate DB
        DB --> DAO: Created
        deactivate DB
        DAO --> UserSvc: User
        deactivate DAO
    else User EXISTS
        UserSvc -> UserSvc: Update OAuth info:\noauthProvider = "google"\noauthId = googleSub\navatar = googlePicture (if newer)
        UserSvc -> DAO: update(existingUser)
        activate DAO
        DAO -> DB: UPDATE Users SET\noauthProvider=?, oauthId=?\nWHERE userId=?
        activate DB
        DB --> DAO: Updated
        deactivate DB
        DAO --> UserSvc: User
        deactivate DAO
    end

    UserSvc --> CallbackCtrl: User (found or created)
    deactivate UserSvc

    == Bước 5: Create Session & Redirect ==

    CallbackCtrl -> CallbackCtrl: session.setAttribute("user", user)\nsession.setAttribute("role", role)
    CallbackCtrl -> DB: INSERT ActivityLogs\n(action='OAUTH_LOGIN', userId)

    CallbackCtrl --> Browser: Redirect → Dashboard\n(theo role user)
    Browser --> User: ✅ Đăng nhập thành công\nvia Google OAuth

end

deactivate CallbackCtrl

@enduml
